# SecureBank Spring Boot Application

A full-stack banking application developed using:

- Spring Boot
- Spring Security + JWT
- Spring Data JPA / Hibernate
- MySQL
- HTML / CSS / JavaScript
- Docker & Docker Compose

## Features

- User Registration & Login
- JWT Authentication
- Create Bank Accounts
- Deposit Money
- Withdraw Money
- Transfer Money
- Transaction History
- Dockerized Deployment

## Tech Stack

Backend:
- Java 17
- Spring Boot
- Hibernate/JPA
- MySQL

Frontend:
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

DevOps:
- Docker
- Docker Compose
- GitHub

## Run Project Using Docker

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

Application:
```text
http://localhost:8080/pages/login.html
```

